    // see the header comment in cm1135.js). Everything past CM1135-166 is
    // beyond the 100-year public-access restriction, so it could not be
    // visually confirmed against the actual scans/finding aid images the way
    // earlier records were - transcribed as given from the MSA guide, warts
    // and all. Only the primary "Nos." certificate range is captured here -
