    //     record immediately before it) ends (01/1946) - almost certainly meant to
    //     read 01/1946, not confirmed, kept exactly as given.
    //   - CM1135-113's date overlaps heavily with CM1135-112's rather than the
    //     usual single-month boundary overlap every other adjacent pair has - kept
